OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGerard Depardieu faces     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsexual assault allegations 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Actor Gerard Depardieu has been accused
OL,6, of sexual assault or harassment by 13  
OL,7, women, according to an investigation by
OL,8, French news website Mediapart.         
OL,10,FThe women claim the star groped them,  
OL,11,Fput his hands in their underwear and   
OL,12,Fmade obscene remarks, the site said.   
OL,14,FThe incidents are alleged to have      
OL,15,Fhappened over the past two decades on  
OL,16,Ffilm and TV sets or in public places.  
OL,18,FA lawyer for Mr Depardieu, 74, said he 
OL,19,F"formally denies all the charges which 
OL,20,Fmay fall under criminal law".          
